			<span class="ht10"></span><span class="ht5 clear"></span><div id="socialIcon"><a href="javascript:;;" onclick="showShareIframe('World AIDS Day: 10 tips for using a condom','http%3A%2F%2Fwww.rediff.com%2Fgetahead%2Fslide-show%2Fslide-show-1-health-world-aids-day-10-tips-for-using-a-condom%2F20111201.htm','getahead','Rediff%20Getahead')" title="Share this article"><div class="othersprite inviteicon">Share<br/>this</div></a>
