				<span class="ht10"></span>
			
			<P><STRONG>2. Check the expiry date</STRONG></P>  <P><FONT size=5>C</FONT>heck the expiry date mentioned for the condoms on the package as they do have a 'use by' date after which, they might not offer you the maximum possible protection.</P>
