											<img title="Next" class="sldnext" alt="Next" src="http://imworld.rediff.com/worldrediff/pix/blank.gif" onclick="moveNext()" />															</td>
				</tr>
				</table>
				<span class="ht10"></span>
			
			<P><STRONG>3. Stock up for holidays</STRONG></P>  <P><FONT size=5>M</FONT>ost people, who travel on holiday travel to foreign shores looking for action and adventure, may face language related or cultural problems, especially in unfamiliar shores. To avoid any difficulty in buying condoms when you're on holiday, stock up on them before you leave home. This will ensure that you can enjoy your vacation responsibly.</P>
			<br/><b>Image: </b>Stock up for holidays<br/><b>Photographs: </b>Uttam Ghosh/Rediff.com			<br/>
