			<P><STRONG>4. Use them before contact</STRONG></P>  <P><FONT size=5>A</FONT>lways ensure that you wear the condom before any physical contact between the penis and the vagina or the anus to prevent the transmission of sexually transmitted diseases or other viruses.</P>
