				<span class="ht10"></span>
			
			<P><STRONG>6. Use a condom every time</STRONG></P>  <P><FONT size=5>U</FONT>sing a condom every single time during sex is the sign of a responsible adult. Even one encounter without a condom can result in STDs (sexually transmitted diseases) and or pregnancy.</P>
