				<span class="ht10"></span>
			
			<P><STRONG>7. Change condoms regularly</STRONG></P>  <P><FONT size=5>I</FONT>f you're having a long session with your partner, ensure that you change your condom for a new one every thirty minutes, as otherwise the chances of breakage will increase multifold, leaving you exposed to the risk of contracting sexually transmitted diseases, not to mention an unwanted pregnancy. </P>  <P>You can also change your condom after ejaculation, if you're up for another round.</P>
